AI-Powered Content Platform

A comprehensive platform that leverages AWS services and GPT-4 API to automatically generate high-quality content for websites, blogs, and marketing materials. The system uses machine learning to analyze user preferences and create tailored content that matches brand voice and style requirements.

Emotion Recognition (EmoBERTa)

EmoBERTa is an advanced natural language processing model built on the RoBERTa architecture that specializes in identifying and analyzing emotional content in text. The model was fine-tuned on a diverse dataset of emotional expressions, achieving state-of-the-art accuracy in emotion detection across multiple languages and contexts.

Portfolio Website

A modern, responsive portfolio website built with React and enhanced with smooth animations. The site features a clean, minimalist design with dark mode aesthetic, interactive elements, and seamless navigation. Backend functionality is powered by a Flask API for contact form submissions and other dynamic features.

React CSS3 AOS Flask Responsive Design JavaScript HTML5 Python REST API

Eternal5 Discord Bot

A custom-built Discord bot designed for gaming communities. It handles music playback from YouTube and Spotify, automates announcements, supports private user queries via DMs, and manages server moderation through role-based commands. Features include music streaming, anonymous DM relay, role-targeted announcements, admin tools, and spam filtering.
